README FOR MANUAL_UPDATE_EMAIL_SENDER.GS

* * SCRIPT DESIGNED FOR USE IN GOOGLE SUITE ONLY - NOT PERSONAL GMAIL ACCOUNTS * *
			some modification is required for use on personal gmail account

- SCRIPT PURPOSE -
Sending an custom automated HTML based email to specified email address via noreply (send only address) 
triggered by button created in google sheets, data fed by highlighted cells.

Script detects highlighted column and scans for items that user has indicated as more than 0 quantity.
Items with 0 quantity will not be included in email body.

- NOTE - 
Script written for specially formatted google sheets document, not universal.